        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1221">
<l>mālaiyō vallai maṇantā ruyiruṇṇum </l>
<l>vēlainī vāḻi poḻutu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Live, O you evening are you (the former) evening? No, you are the season that slays (married) women.</l>
